ng billions of life experience and tips and helped countless people they've never met. The world is big, but we believe people share more similarities in their life than they thought. Safety starts with understanding how developers collect and share your data. No data shared with third parties. This app may collect these data types.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c25277fa5567133d\">>>","score":0.074641936},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5367df399602f1d1\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n美国网民涌进小红书：谁欢迎，谁反对？- DoNews专栏\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5367df399602f1d1\">>>","url":"https://www.donews.com/article/detail/6329/80496.html","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cf2d9656c1624774\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nJanuary 16, 2025 - 这次风波也令一些人联想到2023年7月，Twitter为了推广付费认证业务导致大量海外画师博主大规模迁移微博的事件。当时，Twitter限制未认证用户每天只能刷600条推特，而认证用户（蓝标用户）每天可以阅读6000个帖子。这一政策导致许多插画师的作品热度明显下降，为了维持作品的曝光度和与粉丝的互动，他们纷涌入微博开设账号。\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cf2d9656c1624774\">>>","score":0.07319798},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c6e3e1cef2a0a527\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n小红书笔记不收录怎么解决（看完你就懂了）-加一种草\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c6e3e1cef2a0a527\">>>","url":"https://yx.jiayisiyu.com/blog/post/29036.html","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"02bcc0e1d71382cb\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nJune 9, 2023 - 网友投稿 4099 2023-06-09 · 经常在群里看到有小伙伴问小红书笔记收录相关的情况：“为什么搜不到自己的笔记？”、“怎么才能知道自己的笔记有没有被收录？”、“笔记没有收录应该怎么办”……\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"02bcc0e1d71382cb\">>>","score":0.058286972},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3cf1474c514afd9b\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n小红书审查百科：舆情日报 - China Digital Space\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3cf1474c514afd9b\">>>","url":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/小红书审查百科：舆情日报","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"db974d32fcf3aade\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nTuesday, February 10, 2026 · 本页面是小红书审查wiki泄露文件的一部分，全部文件请参看小红书审查百科。\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUST