{"type":"message","id":"b63ff042","parentId":"15c7f834","timestamp":"2026-03-28T09:00:17.349Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户现在说要使用小红书的skill直接帮他发布内容，首先我需要检查有没有对应的小红书相关的技能，看之前的available_skills里，哦，之前的技能列表里没有专门的小红书发布的skill？不对，看之前的skill列表里有没有相关的？哦，之前的技能里有xiaohongshu-mcp？不对，看一下：哦，有个xiaohongshu-mcp的skill，功能是小红书内容自动化发布。不对，再看用户的要求，首先我需要先确认有没有对应的发布工具，哦，看系统提供的工具里有没有小红书发布的工具？哦，系统给的工具里有message？不对，message是发消息的，哦，不对，之前的available_skills里有个xiaohongshu-mcp的skill对吧？看一下：<skill>\n    <name>xiaohongshu-mcp</name>\n    <description>Automate Xiaohongshu (RedNote) content operations using a Python client for the xiaohongshu-mcp server. Use for: (1) Publishing image, text, and video content, (2) Searching for notes and trends, (3) Analyzing post details and comments, (4) Managing user profiles and content feeds. Triggers: xiaohongshu automation, rednote content, publish to xiaohongshu, xiaohongshu search, social media management.\n</description>\n    <location>~/.openclaw\\skills\\xiaohongshu-mcp\\SKILL.md</location>\n  </skill>\n对，有这个skill，所以首先我需要先读取这个skill的SKILL.md，了解怎么使用它来发布内容。所以接下来调用read工具读取这个skill的文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dz66zitvy5lntx02kacz4nub","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/xiaohongshu-mcp/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":96964,"output":803,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97767,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774688403178,"responseId":"0217746884045212748f57c5f4210b3bc611acce6828c7a58221b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b5cb2efe","parentId":"b63ff042","timestamp":"2026-03-28T09:00:17.357Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_dz66zitvy5lntx02kacz4nub","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: xiaohongshu-mcp\ndescription: >\n  Automate Xiaohongshu (RedNote) content operations using a Python client for the xiaohongshu-mcp server.\n  Use for: (1) Publishing image, text, and video content, (2) Searching for notes and trends,\n  (3) Analyzing post details and comments, (4) Managing user profiles and content feeds.\n  Triggers: xiaohongshu automation, rednote content, publish to xiaohongshu, xiaohongshu search, social media management.\n---\n\n# Xiaohongshu MCP Skill (with Python Client)\n\nAutomate content operations on Xiaohongshu (小红书) using a bundled Python script that interacts with the `xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp` server (8.4k+ stars).\n\n**Project:** [xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp](https://github.com/xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp)\n\n## 1. Local Server Setup\n\nThis skill requires the `xiaohongshu-mcp` server to be running on your local machine.\n\n### Step 1: Download Binaries\n\nDownload the appropriate binaries for your system from the [GitHub Releases](https://github.com/xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp/releases) page.\n\n| Platform | MCP Server | Login Tool |\n| -------- | ---------- | ---------- |\n| macOS (Apple Silicon) | `xiaohongshu-mcp-darwin-arm64` | `xiaohongshu-login-darwin-arm64` |\n| macOS (Intel) | `xiaohongshu-mcp-darwin-amd64` | `xiaohongshu-login-darwin-amd64` |\n| Windows | `xiaohongshu-mcp-windows-amd64.exe` | `xiaohongshu-login-windows-amd64.exe` |\n| Linux | `xiaohongshu-mcp-linux-amd64` | `xiaohongshu-login-linux-amd64` |\n\nGrant execute permission to the downloaded files:\n```shell\nchmod +x xiaohongshu-mcp-darwin-arm64 xiaohongshu-login-darwin-arm64\n```\n\n### Step 2: Login (First Time Only)\n\nRun the login tool. It will open a browser window with a QR code. Scan it with your Xiaohongshu mobile app.\n\n```shell\n./xiaohongshu-login-darwin-arm64\n```\n\n> **Important**: Do not log into the same Xiaohongshu account on any other web browser, as this will invalidate the server's session.\n\n### Step 3: Start the MCP Server\n\nRun the MCP server in a separate terminal window. It will run in the background.\n\n```shell\n# Run in headless mode (recommended)\n./xiaohongshu-mcp-darwin-arm64\n\n# Or, run with a visible browser for debugging\n./xiaohongshu-mcp-darwin-arm64 -headless=false\n```\n\nThe server will be available at `http://localhost:18060`.\n\n## 2. Using the Skill\n\nThis skill includes a Python client (`scripts/xhs_client.py`) to interact with the local server. You can use it directly from the shell.\n\n### Available Commands\n\n| Command | Description | Example |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `status` | Check login status | `python scripts/xhs_client.py status` |\n| `search <keyword>` | Search for notes | `python scripts/xhs_client.py search \"咖啡\"` |\n| `detail <id> <token>` | Get note details | `python scripts/xhs_client.py detail \"note_id\" \"xsec_token\"` |\n| `feeds` | Get recommended feed | `python scripts/xhs_client.py feeds` |\n| `publish <title> <content> <images>` | Publish a note | `python scripts/xhs_client.py publish \"Title\" \"Content\" \"url1,url2\"` |\n\n### Example Workflow: Market Research\n\n1.  **Check Status**: First, ensure the server is running and you are logged in.\n    ```shell\n    python ~/clawd/skills/xiaohongshu-mcp/scripts/xhs_client.py status\n    ```\n\n2.  **Search for a Keyword**: Find notes related to your research topic. The output will include the `feed_id` and `xsec_token` needed for the next step.\n    ```shell\n    python ~/clawd/skills/xiaohongshu-mcp/scripts/xhs_client.py search \"户外电源\"\n    ```\n\n3.  **Get Note Details**: Use the `feed_id` and `xsec_token` from the search results to get the full content and comments of a specific note.\n    ```shell\n    python ~/clawd/skills/xiaohongshu-mcp/scripts/xhs_client.py detail \"64f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\" \"security_token_here\"\n    ```\n\n4.  **Analyze**: Review the note's content, comments, and engagement data to gather insights.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774688417356}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef4e4854","parentId":"b5cb2efe","timestamp":"2026-03-28T09:00:31.502Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户现在想要直接发布小红书帖子，但根据这个skill的说明，首先需要先搭建本地的xiaohongshu-mcp服务，还要登录扫码，这些是前置条件，我得先告诉用户这些准备步骤，然后等用户完成了再帮忙发布。首先要清晰说明需要做的准备：\n1. 先去github下载对应Windows版本的服务端和登录工具\n2. 扫码登录账号\n3. 启动服务\n然后等用户完成这些之后，就可以调用命令发布刚才的那篇内容了。现在先把操作步骤清晰告诉用户，按照Windows系统的情况来写。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"要帮你自动发布小红书笔记，需要先完成3步前置准备（只需要做一次，之后就可以一键发布所有内容了）：\n\n### 📝 准备步骤（Windows系统）：\n1. **下载工具包**\n   去GitHub下载对应Windows的两个文件：\n   - 服务端：`xiaohongshu-mcp-windows-amd64.exe`\n   - 登录工具：`xiaohongshu-login-windows-amd64.exe`\n   下载地址：https://github.com/xpzouying/xiaohongshu-mcp/releases\n\n2. **登录你的小红书账号**\n   双击运行`xiaohongshu-login-windows-amd64.exe`，会弹出二维码，用你手机上的小红书APP扫码登录即可（登录后不要在其他浏览器登同一个小红书账号，会掉会话）\n\n3. **启动本地服务**\n   双击运行`xiaohongshu-mcp-windows-amd64.exe`，保持这个窗口开着不要关，服务就启动好了\n\n### 完成后告诉我，我会直接帮你把刚才的检查攻略笔记一键发布，后面所有内容都可以自动发，不用你手动复制粘贴了~"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":2493,"output":533,"cacheRead":96056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99082,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774688417358,"responseId":"0217746884185278f8ea30227d9931fee346cda39788dd1c654fd"}}
