{"type":"message","id":"49dc7ba7","parentId":"a023703d","timestamp":"2026-03-28T09:50:01.313Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户给了一个小红书短链接，需要先解析出里面的帖子ID，首先先获取这个短链接的跳转地址，提取出item后面的ID，然后才能执行删除操作。首先用web_fetch或者exec curl来解析短链接？不对，应该用curl命令去获取这个短链接的跳转目标，这样就能拿到真实的URL，然后提取帖子ID。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_lhpn80zprrxl1ayprzosezhr","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -I \"http://xhslink.com/o/A2Itcx642QG\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":95314,"output":214,"cacheRead":22328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117856,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774691387768,"responseId":"021774691389146bec3f42aa889c5b9258a8a5e9d4b8deaf4e799"}}
